name: Caning Label "Enjoy" Stamp
description:
Perfect for stamping onto any scrap piece of paper and turning it into a canning label.
A perfect addition to your food gifts or just to brighten up your own pantry!

Works for regular and wide mouth lids. Simply stamp, trace and cut! You can also make circles with a circle punch and then stamp or use circular stickers. 

Finished size: aprox 2.5 x 2.5
Art Mount Wood Stamp
High Quality Red Rubber
Delivered in a muslin bag
